Obtain Geographic Layer

cha_layer.Rd

Import geographic layer as a sf object.

Usage

cha_layer(layer_key, progress = TRUE)

Arguments

layer_key

Unique ID for a geographic layer.

progress

Display a progress bar?

Value

sf geographic layer.

Examples

cha_layer("zip")
